          <physDesc>
            <objectDesc>
              <supportDesc>
                <extent>1 online resource (2 bifolia)</extent>
                <foliation>Pagination in ink in Hindu-Arabic numerals (658-661; 702-705); modern pagination added in pencil, upper outer corners (1A-4B) as if the leaves were to be read left-to-right; catchwords every verso, lower left. Order of digital images follows pagination in ink.</foliation>
              </supportDesc>
              <layoutDesc>
                <layout>Written in 13-17 lines in two columns with a third column of 12 angled lines; ruled with a misṭarah.</layout>
              </layoutDesc>
            </objectDesc>
